<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, viewport-fit=cover">
  <title>AI Disclosure Notice | GetPawsy</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles.css">
  <style>
    .legal-page { max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 40px 20px; }
    .legal-page h1 { color: var(--pawsy-primary, #6366f1); margin-bottom: 10px; }
    .legal-page .last-updated { color: #666; font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 30px; }
    .legal-page h2 { color: #333; margin: 30px 0 15px; border-bottom: 2px solid #f0f0f0; padding-bottom: 10px; }
    .legal-page p, .legal-page li { line-height: 1.8; color: #444; }
    .legal-page ul { padding-left: 25px; margin: 15px 0; }
    .legal-page .highlight { background: #f8f9ff; padding: 20px; border-radius: 12px; border-left: 4px solid var(--pawsy-primary, #6366f1); margin: 20px 0; }
    .legal-page .ai-card { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f8f9ff 0%, #e8e0ff 100%); padding: 25px; border-radius: 16px; margin: 20px 0; }
    .legal-page .ai-card h3 { margin-top: 0; color: var(--pawsy-primary, #6366f1); }
    .legal-page .ai-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr)); gap: 20px; margin: 30px 0; }
    .legal-page .rights-box { background: #f0fdf4; padding: 20px; border-radius: 12px; border-left: 4px solid #22c55e; margin: 20px 0; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <%- include('../partials/header') %>

  <main class="legal-page">
    <h1>AI Disclosure Notice</h1>
    <p class="last-updated">Last Updated: December 2024</p>

    <div class="highlight">
      <p><strong>Transparency Commitment:</strong> At GetPawsy, we believe in being open about our use of artificial intelligence. This notice explains how we use AI technology to serve you better and what your rights are.</p>
    </div>

    <h2>How We Use Artificial Intelligence</h2>
    <p>GetPawsy utilizes AI technology in several ways to enhance your shopping experience:</p>

    <div class="ai-grid">
      <div class="ai-card">
        <h3>Customer Support</h3>
        <p><strong>Pawsy AI Chatbot</strong></p>
        <ul>
          <li>24/7 instant customer support</li>
          <li>Answers questions about products, orders, shipping</li>
          <li>Voice input and output capabilities</li>
          <li>Conversational, personalized assistance</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="ai-card">
        <h3>Product Recommendations</h3>
        <p><strong>Smart Recommendations Engine</strong></p>
        <ul>
          <li>Analyzes browsing and purchase history</li>
          <li>Suggests relevant products for your pet</li>
          <li>Personalized upsell and cross-sell suggestions</li>
          <li>Category-based recommendations</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="ai-card">
        <h3>Pricing & Promotions</h3>
        <p><strong>Dynamic Pricing Engine</strong></p>
        <ul>
          <li>Optimizes pricing based on market conditions</li>
          <li>Creates personalized discount offers</li>
          <li>Manages flash sales and promotions</li>
          <li>Ensures competitive pricing</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="ai-card">
        <h3>Returns Processing</h3>
        <p><strong>AI Returns Assistant</strong></p>
        <ul>
          <li>Evaluates return requests automatically</li>
          <li>Risk scoring for fraud prevention</li>
          <li>Instant approval for low-risk returns</li>
          <li>Escalates complex cases to humans</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="ai-card">
        <h3>Fraud Detection</h3>
        <p><strong>Security AI System</strong></p>
        <ul>
          <li>Monitors for fraudulent transactions</li>
          <li>Analyzes purchase patterns</li>
          <li>Protects your account security</li>
          <li>Prevents chargebacks and abuse</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="ai-card">
        <h3>Voice Interactions</h3>
        <p><strong>Speech Recognition</strong></p>
        <ul>
          <li>Voice input for chatbot conversations</li>
          <li>Text-to-speech for responses</li>
          <li>Hands-free shopping assistance</li>
          <li>Accessibility support</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <h2>AI Technology Partners</h2>
    <p>Our AI features are powered by industry-leading technology:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>OpenAI:</strong> Natural language processing for chatbot and content generation</li>
      <li><strong>Custom ML Models:</strong> Proprietary models for recommendations and fraud detection</li>
      <li><strong>Web Speech API:</strong> Browser-based voice recognition and synthesis</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Data Used by AI Systems</h2>
    <p>Our AI systems may process:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Your browsing history on our website</li>
      <li>Purchase history and order details</li>
      <li>Product searches and wishlist items</li>
      <li>Chat conversations with Pawsy AI</li>
      <li>Review and feedback you provide</li>
      <li>Account preferences and settings</li>
    </ul>
    <p>For full details on data collection, see our <a href="/legal/privacy">Privacy Policy</a>.</p>

    <h2>Your Rights Regarding AI</h2>
    <div class="rights-box">
      <h3>You Have the Right To:</h3>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Human Review:</strong> Request human review of any automated decision that significantly affects you</li>
        <li><strong>Explanation:</strong> Receive an explanation of how AI arrived at a decision</li>
        <li><strong>Opt-Out:</strong> Disable personalized AI recommendations (affects experience)</li>
        <li><strong>Data Access:</strong> See what data AI systems have about you</li>
        <li><strong>Correction:</strong> Request corrections to inaccurate data used by AI</li>
        <li><strong>Deletion:</strong> Request deletion of AI-processed data (subject to limitations)</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <h2>Limitations of AI</h2>
    <p>We want you to understand that AI systems:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>May occasionally make errors or provide imperfect recommendations</li>
      <li>Are tools that assist human decision-making, not replace it</li>
      <li>Are continuously improved based on feedback</li>
      <li>Cannot replace professional advice (veterinary, legal, etc.)</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Human Oversight</h2>
    <p>GetPawsy maintains human oversight of AI systems:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Customer service team reviews complex chatbot escalations</li>
      <li>Returns team reviews flagged return requests</li>
      <li>Fraud team investigates AI-flagged transactions</li>
      <li>Regular audits of AI decision accuracy and fairness</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Ethical AI Commitment</h2>
    <p>We are committed to responsible AI use:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Fairness:</strong> AI systems are designed to treat all customers equitably</li>
      <li><strong>Transparency:</strong> We clearly disclose when you're interacting with AI</li>
      <li><strong>Privacy:</strong> AI data processing follows our Privacy Policy</li>
      <li><strong>Security:</strong> AI systems are protected with industry-standard security</li>
      <li><strong>Continuous Improvement:</strong> We regularly review and improve AI accuracy</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Future AI Features</h2>
    <p>We may introduce new AI features in the future. When we do, we will:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Update this disclosure notice</li>
      <li>Notify you of significant changes</li>
      <li>Provide opt-out options where appropriate</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Questions or Concerns</h2>
    <p>If you have questions about our AI use or want to exercise your rights:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Email: ai@getpawsy.com</li>
      <li>Email: privacy@getpawsy.com</li>
      <li>Visit: <a href="/contact">Contact Page</a></li>
    </ul>

    <p style="margin-top: 40px; padding: 20px; background: #f8f9ff; border-radius: 12px; text-align: center;">
      <strong>Our Promise:</strong> AI at GetPawsy is designed to serve you better, not replace human care. We're here to helpâ€”just ask!
    </p>
  </main>

  <%- include('../partials/footer') %>
</body>
</html>
